<sect1 id="yelp" xreflabel="Yelp-&yelp-version;">
  <?dbhtml filename="yelp.html"?>


  <title>Yelp-&yelp-version;</title>

  <indexterm zone="yelp">
    <primary sortas="a-Yelp">Yelp</primary>
  </indexterm>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introdução a Yelp</title>

    <para>
      The <application>Yelp</application> package contains a help browser used for
viewing help files.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Informação do Pacote</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Transferência (HTTP): <ulink url="&yelp-download-http;"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Transferência (FTP): <ulink url="&yelp-download-ftp;"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Soma de verificação MD5: &yelp-md5sum;
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Tamanho da transferência: &yelp-size;
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Espaço em disco estimado exigido: &yelp-buildsize;
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Tempo de construção estimado: &yelp-time;
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Dependências de Yelp</bridgehead>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Exigida</bridgehead>
    <para role="required">
      <xref linkend="gsettings-desktop-schemas"/>, <xref linkend="webkitgtk"/> and
<xref linkend="yelp-xsl"/>
    </para>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Recomendada</bridgehead>
    <para role="recommended">
      <xref linkend="desktop-file-utils"/>
    </para>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Opcionais</bridgehead>
    <para role="optional">
      <xref linkend="gtk-doc"/>
    </para>

    <note>
      <para>
        The <application>Yelp</application> package is not required for a functional
<application>GNOME</application> Desktop. Note, however, that without
<application>Yelp</application> you will not be able to view the built-in
Help provided by core <application>GNOME</application> and many of the
support applications.
      </para>
    </note>

    <para condition="html" role="usernotes">Observações de Usuário(a): <ulink url="&blfs-wiki;/yelp"/>
    </para>
  </sect2>

  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Instalação de Yelp</title>

    <para>
      Instale <application>Yelp</application> executando os seguintes comandos:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr --disable-static &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Esse pacote não vem com uma suíte de teste.
    </para>

    <para>
      Agora, como o(a) usuário(a) <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Still as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user, ensure
that <filename>/usr/share/applications/mimeinfo.cache</filename> will be
updated and therefore the <command>help</command> in gnome applications will
work.
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>update-desktop-database</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

